  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open World Island</strong>: Lavender Island takes place in an open world city with five distinct neighborhoods.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wild Quests</strong>: Eccentric characters give you off-the-wall tasks and missions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Interactions</strong>: The lives of people on Lavender Island are bleak. Maybe hearing their story will help you?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simulated Movie</strong>: Ever wanted to watch a whole movie inside a whole game? Your time is now, your place is here.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alien Anatomy</strong>: Some aliens have two butts and two mouths. I know, it's crazy, just go with it.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/812a461b10661e87856c4424d87979e6.poster.avif?t=1766779553\" width=780 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/812a461b10661e87856c4424d87979e6.webm?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/812a461b10661e87856c4424d87979e6.mp4?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a dream that refuses to end. As Zede Aksis, wander a surreal city that feels both alive and liminal, filled with digital citizens and absurd infrastructure. Can you find an escape? A way out of a world that remembers you better than you remember it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/6b13fbd586cd45572d2bd2b7d202486e.poster.avif?t=1766779553\" width=780 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/6b13fbd586cd45572d2bd2b7d202486e.webm?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/6b13fbd586cd45572d2bd2b7d202486e.mp4?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a city shaped by memory and code-- where the streetlights hum lullabies, and stairways spiral into forgotten neighborhoods. Escape from Lavender Island is an open-world exploration of the subconscious, a place where the unknown constantly unfolds before you. Every corner feels familiar, but nothing looks like you remember.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/100c9dd50238caeeceb0e65d47ee7487.poster.avif?t=1766779553\" width=780 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/100c9dd50238caeeceb0e65d47ee7487.webm?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/100c9dd50238caeeceb0e65d47ee7487.mp4?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a game about being lost in the in-between: the space between dreams and waking, between knowing who you are and who you might’ve been. As Zede, you collect fragments of language, art, and architecture that hint at a life outside the simulation-- but the deeper you go, the more the island reshapes to fit you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/febf2979b778741eb18451978f5dbd80.poster.avif?t=1766779553\" width=780 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/febf2979b778741eb18451978f5dbd80.webm?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164310/extras/febf2979b778741eb18451978f5dbd80.mp4?t=1766779553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world itself is the story. The Lavender Corporation, an evil group from the mainland, works with an alien civilization to control the island and everyone who lives on it. To fight back, you'll accept missions, meet contacts, and find masks with different abilities.</p>",
